@beforeEach and @afterEach

@beforeEach -->it executes for every test case before .
  -->Runs  Before EVERY test.
@AfterEach--> it executes for every test case after.
  --> Runs  After EVERY test.

@BeforeAll and After ALL
@beforeAll -->use static and it will run only once before all the test cases.
@AfterAll  -->use static and it will run only once after all the test cases.
THese 2 are independent of instances and indpendent of objects. thats why we use 
static keyword.








